---
title: Mushroom & Lentil Shepherd's Pie with Plant-Based Parmesan Mash Topping & Garlicky Greens
description: Haven't found the umami you've been looking for? That elusive fifth ‘savoury’ flavour is bursting out of this pie thanks to the
mushroom powder in the lentil filling and the plant-based Parmesan stirred through the creamy mash topping. Enjoy!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
